  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to demonstrate the efficacy and safety of donepezil on the
      recovery of cognitive function in patients with stroke and to delineate the neurophysiologic
      mechanisms of the therapeutic effect of donepezil on the recovery of cognitive network using
      functional neuroimaging technique.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
